summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Kennedy's Acre Tracts Division No. 2; Northeast Quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East; Hurstwood First Division; Northeast Quarter of Section 13, Township 26 North, Range 3 East; Seattle Suburban Home Tracts Southeast Quarter of Section 17, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; and Park View Tracts.
